Title: Not a Heating Pack
Description:
Tharessa has done some reconnaissance for us and found the gorlocs are digging up artifacts and... cuddling with them. 

I think it means that the artifacts emit heat? Maybe that means some artifacts are still functioning?

Imagine--the titans created technology to shape worlds, and now a fish uses it to warm their fins. Hah!

The gorlocs won't give them up, and I don't want to be a Rannan-kabob either. I hate to ask because they just want to be warm, but could you do something about them?
ObjectivesText: Rannan wants you to kill 12 gorlocs.
CompletionText: Did you get them? I thought I saw one sneak by a moment ago...
RewardText: Wonderful! Now we can focus our attention on what really matters--the artifacts. I wonder what we will discover?
